How to build this plugin

1. Create a new project in Android Studio
2. Select 'Add No Activity'
3. Select 'File > New Module' to create a new JavaLibrary
4. Copy display4k/src/main/java/com/YourCompanyName/UnityPluginDisplay4k.java to your java library
5. Copy display4k/build.gradle to your java library
6. Open Terminal in Android Studio and change the current directory to your java library
7. Run `../gradlew jar` to build jar file
